---
layout: base.njk
permalink: /blog/index.html
title: Blog — Points Harvest
description: Tips, updates, and guides from the Points Harvest team.
extraStyles:
  - /prose.css
---

  <div class="blog-header">
    <div class="section-label">Blog</div>
    <h1>Tips &amp; Updates</h1>
    <p>Guides, release notes, and Bing Rewards tips from the Points Harvest team.</p>
  </div>

  <hr class="section-divider" />

  <div class="post-list">
    {%- if collections.posts.length %}
    {%- for post in collections.posts %}
      <article class="post-card">
        <div class="post-meta">{{ post.date | formatDate }}</div>
        <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
        <p class="post-summary">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <a class="read-more" href="{{ post.url }}">Read more &rarr;</a>
      </article>
    {%- endfor %}
    {%- else %}
    <p class="no-posts">No posts yet — check back soon.</p>
    {%- endif %}
  </div>
